---
/**
 * ContactSection — 联系方式区块
 */
---

<section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pb-20">
  <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
    <h2 class="text-parchment/25 text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-wider">联系方式</h2>
    <div class="flex-1 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-white/[0.08] to-transparent"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="panel-glass p-6">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
      <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-gold/10 border border-gold/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
        <iconify-icon icon="lucide:mail" width="18" height="18" class="text-gold/70"></iconify-icon>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-parchment/60 text-sm font-heading">邮箱</p>
        <a href="mailto:praxiswalker@gmail.com" class="text-parchment/35 hover:text-bio-cyan text-xs mt-0.5 font-mono no-underline">
          praxiswalker@gmail.com
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="text-parchment/30 text-xs mt-4 leading-relaxed">
      如果你对某个 Idea 感兴趣，或者想聊聊 AI、内容创作和技术，欢迎联系。
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
